commit.message:
Upgrade cabal package description format to 2.0

This is to avoid warnings with a fixed cabal-version field, which is now
required on Hackage.

Change cabal-version from range to fixed version.

Newer cabal versions no longer support a range for cabal-version.
Hackage will reject packages using a range in cabal-version.
